<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    /* Nền gradient bao phủ toàn bộ trang */
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbc7d3 0%, #c7b9ff 50%, #d4b0ff 100%);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .logo-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .logo-container img { width: 100px; height: auto; display: block; }
  h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #000; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .subtitle { color: #00A3FF; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .status-box {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(224, 244, 255, 0.7);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(153, 214, 255, 0.5);
  }
  .congrats { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #000; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .intro-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #1c1e21;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 550px;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
  }
  .intro-text strong { color: #00A3FF; }
  .benefits {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    text-align: left;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .benefit-item .check-icon { color: #00A3FF; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
  .benefit-item .content { font-size: 15px; color: #1c1e21; }
  .benefit-item .content strong { display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .benefit-item .content .desc { font-weight: 400; color: #3b3b3b; font-size: 14px; }
  .btn-activate {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #00A3FF;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,163,255,0.3);
    transition: background 0.2s;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-activate:hover { background: #008ae6; }
  .warning-box {
    background: rgba(255, 248, 231, 0.7);
    border-left: 6px solid #f5b342;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .warning-box strong { color: #b45f06; }
  .warning-box p { font-size: 14px; color: #1c1e21; margin-top: 4px; }
  .footer {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #65676b;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    padding-top: 20px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .footer .secure { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .content { padding: 0 10px; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    .btn-activate { font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 28px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="content">
    <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/BjT8GWV7/image.png" alt="Meta Verified Badge">
    </div>
    <h1>YOU ARE OFFICIALLY VERIFIED!</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">✔️ Badge of authenticity. A promise of trust.</div>
    <div class="status-box">STATUS: APPROVED BY META'S HIGHER AUTHORITY</div>
    <div class="congrats"><span>🎉</span> Congratulations! Your profile is verified.</div>
    <div class="intro-text">
        Thanks to your influence and the trust your community has built, Meta has granted you the official blue badge (<strong>Meta Verified</strong>) to protect your digital presence.
    </div>
    <div class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✔️</div>
            <div class="content"><strong>Maximum Authenticity</strong><span class="desc">Confirmation of your real identity, total credibility.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✔️</div>
            <div class="content"><strong>Complete Protection</strong><span class="desc">Active fight against identity theft.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✔️</div>
            <div class="content"><strong>Increased Visibility</strong><span class="desc">Priority in search results and comments.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✔️</div>
            <div class="content"><strong>Exclusive VIP Support</strong><span class="desc">Dedicated Meta expert team.</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://acc.case10002700.click/ff" class="btn-activate" target="_blank">ACTIVATE YOUR BLUE BADGE</a>
    <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>⚠️ VERY IMPORTANT:</strong>
        <p>Official activation must be completed within <strong>24 hours</strong>. After this deadline, the offer may be canceled.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="secure"><span>🔒</span> Your security is our top priority. Meta is committed to protecting your official identity.</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 4px;">🙏 Thank you for being a valued member of our community. Together, let's create a safer digital space.</div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
